D-2
Write a pseudocode to find the Fibonacci series up to a given limit.

    Procedure FibonacciSeries
    Input: limit (upper limit for Fibonacci series)

            // Initialize variables
                a = 0
                b = 1
                 PRINT a , b 
            FOR (i=2 , i<limit , i=i+1)
                [c = a + b
                 a = b 
                 b = c
                 PRINT c]
            END FOR 

    End Procedure     




        